      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six, maintaining factory compression across all cylinders and a pristine double-VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, notch-free shifts, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity under high torque loads. Every suspension bushing is factory-spec, preserving the original kinematics and communicative steering rack. The rod bearings have been addressed as a preventative measure, and the limited-slip differential operates silently. Visually and mechanically, this vehicle is free of any deferred maintenance or cosmetic wear, representing the pinnacle of atmospheric M-division performance.",
